00:11:18.660 --> 00:11:30.900
It's really interesting to hear that it was so impactful, and I know it was a long journey.

00:11:30.900 --> 00:11:36.980
Long journey, yeah. I told one of my friends as well, she was really excited, she wanted to come

00:11:36.980 --> 00:11:44.340
and see the museum when I told her it reminded my back home and what we used to do with it,

00:11:44.340 --> 00:11:48.340
and it reminded me good things and bad as well.

00:11:49.620 --> 00:11:56.580
So how we, it was good like we was as a family doing everything, I was with my family, but

00:11:57.780 --> 00:12:06.820
now I'm here by myself, so it's a bit, you know, you remember those things, yeah.

00:12:08.660 --> 00:12:10.180
It's both happy and painful, isn't it?

00:12:10.180 --> 00:12:11.620
Yes, it is.

00:12:11.620 --> 00:12:12.900
Happy to have those memories.

00:12:12.900 --> 00:12:19.220
Memories, yeah, but it is a little bit struggle life, you know.

00:12:20.980 --> 00:12:22.420
Do you mean when you were younger it was?

00:12:23.220 --> 00:12:33.380
It was hard, it was very hard. I don't want my, I want my children to learn this kind of thing,

00:12:33.380 --> 00:12:35.780
but not forced to do something.

00:12:38.020 --> 00:12:39.220
Yeah, yeah.

00:12:40.020 --> 00:12:46.660
It wasn't like for us easy, it's like from ourself we wanted to learn to do some. Now my children,

00:12:46.660 --> 00:12:51.940
if they wanted they will say, oh mom, can we do that? Can we help you in the cooking? But

00:12:52.580 --> 00:12:58.260
for us it wasn't like we wanted, it was all by force, you have to

00:13:00.580 --> 00:13:06.660
do this thing, so it was really hard because during whole week we have to do that.

00:13:07.620 --> 00:13:12.340
It's like if we get time even for the studies it will be in the night time,

00:13:13.700 --> 00:13:16.660
and again from morning we will start doing the same thing.

00:13:17.700 --> 00:13:22.260
