00:13:23.540 --> 00:13:31.060
Because schools start from seven o'clock in the morning, so when we, they wake us from the prayer

00:13:31.060 --> 00:13:36.900
then we sit down and whatever we can help with the cooking and everything, breakfast.

00:13:38.020 --> 00:13:39.380
And then school all day.

00:13:39.380 --> 00:13:43.860
School all day and when we come back from the school straight away we do help.

00:13:45.220 --> 00:13:46.500
That's a lot isn't it?

00:13:46.500 --> 00:13:47.000
A lot.

