we can't get what we wanted and if we dress up always we have to be long, proper so it wasn't

00:15:04.900 --> 00:15:13.860
like free freedom what you get it, no. But we have to do everything strictly, listen,

00:15:14.580 --> 00:15:18.820
listen in a way if not then we will be banned.

00:15:20.660 --> 00:15:26.980
We cannot only do works only, nothing we can do.

00:15:30.820 --> 00:15:33.460
Is there anything else about your childhood you'd like to share?

00:15:36.420 --> 00:15:38.180
